  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Prioritize forward motion in 'clear' state to maximize area coverage.",
    "Upon obstacle detection, initiate systematic avoidance (rotate away from obstacle, then move forward).",
    "Introduce 'avoid_left' and 'avoid_right' to prevent oscillations and encourage side-stepping.",
    "Trigger 'full_scan' after repeated obstacle encounters to reorient and find new coverage direction.",
    "Return to 'clear' as soon as path is open to resume coverage.",
    "Permit random_walk as a fallback to escape local minima or deadlocks."
